CREATE TABLE cards ( card_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, user_id UUID NOT NULL, card_number STRING NOT NULL, expiry_date DATE NOT NULL, cvv INTEGER NOT NULL, FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id) );
